By pressing “Fields,” you can choose the fields according to which documents are grouped. Some fields are mandatory and selected by default.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000635-0/EN_Fields1.png"><br>

{{% alert title="NOTE" color="warning" %}}
To generate an invoice for each delivery note, check the Document No. field.
{{% /alert %}}

